Notes:
BOAF contained quotes from The Birds. During Lawn Boy, Page walked all the way over and said hello to "Mike Side." Weekapaug included Crosseyed quotes and a NMINML tease. During the Weekapaug jam, Trey and Mike stood face to face before turning to the front of the stage and stepping in unison with the music.
